        <name>VersionId</name>
        <qualifiedname>helios::core::types::VersionId</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Version number for detecting stale entity references. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Each entity slot in an EntityPool has an associated version that is incremented when the entity is removed. EntityHandles store both the <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1core_1_1types_1ae66a87b0172199142b048c268bf0b18a" kindref="member">EntityId</ref> and <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1core_1_1types_1a0b0725c2e899452c00381f709d463746" kindref="member">VersionId</ref>, allowing the pool to detect when a handle refers to a recycled slot.</para>
<para>A valid version starts at 1 (uninitialized handles have version 0).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>EntityHandle </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1core_1_1types_1ae66a87b0172199142b048c268bf0b18a" kindref="member">EntityId</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>EntityPool </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
